{"tid":533703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小室哲哉被爆婚外情, 宣佈退出演藝界","createTime":"2018-01-19T05:25:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T05:31:03.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a7f490ca9ffd27b8d9df1b218922052e6f103946","tid":533703,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:25:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180119/57726919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57726919&d=Q26sThRywBPecVqUHaKi6DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=10424c22\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57726919&h=4c119eff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180119/57726919</a><br />\n<br />\n【開記招謝罪】小室哲哉被爆婚外情 宣佈退出演藝界<br />\n<br />\n26,068<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0119 12:36<br />\n<br />\n現年59歲嘅日本昔日樂壇教父小室哲哉，被雜誌《週刊文春》踢爆背着結婚15年嘅患病妻子、globe主音KEIKO，搭上一名貌似柴咲幸嘅美女護士A小姐，佢因近日爆出不倫戀醜聞，今日終於開記者會公開鞠躬道歉，小室在會上向KEIKO及公眾道歉，還表示在圈中感到疲累，並因今次事件決定退出演藝界。<br />\n<br />\n今日記者會，小室穿上西裝憔悴現身，佢否認跟A小姐有越軌關係，小室在會上說：「對KEIKO、家人、歌迷及工作人員感到擔心而抱歉，就今次報道，我已決定引退。」小室曾在日本樂壇點石成金，曾捧紅安室奈美惠、TRF、globe、華原朋美及鈴木亞美等，小室家族在90年代可謂紅遍亞洲。<br />\n<br />\n講到小室退出娛樂圈，曾經係其徒弟嘅陳敏之今日回應傳媒：「其實同小室好多年冇見啦，對於佢私人事，唔回應喇，即係佢感情事嗰啲。至於佢退出娛樂圈，佢決定得都有佢原因嘅，我祝福佢日後生活健康愉快。」"},{"pid":"44afc7a262ce0ce50a11e8960d25f8c74446c5b1","tid":533703,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我同佢唔係好熟</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1948d3659887c2e60ab0a0480e88d8a02013320e","tid":533703,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44afc7a262ce0ce50a11e8960d25f8c74446c5b1","tid":533703,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:26:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我同佢唔係好熟</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}